% ===================== RADIAL SURFACES =====================
surf sPel  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.39218    % fuel pellet
surf sGap  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40005    % gap
surf sClad cyl 0.0 0.0 0.45720    % clad / structural rod OD
surf sSpr  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.06459    % plenum spring (Inconel)
surf sGtIn cyl 0.0 0.0 0.56134    % guide tube inner
surf sGtOu cyl 0.0 0.0 0.60198    % guide tube outer
surf sDpIn cyl 0.0 0.0 0.50419    % dashpot thimble inner
surf sDpOu cyl 0.0 0.0 0.54610    % dashpot thimble outer
surf sItA  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.43688    % instrument air / BA He
surf sItZ1 cyl 0.0 0.0 0.48387    % instrument inner Zr / BA SS outer
surf sBa1  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.21400    % BA air
surf sBa2  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.23051    % BA SS inner
surf sBa3  cyl 0.0 0.0 0.24130    % BA He
surf sBaPy cyl 0.0 0.0 0.42672    % BA pyrex
surf sGin  sqc 0.0 0.0 0.61015    % thick grid inner half-width
surf sGout sqc 0.0 0.0 0.62992    % thick grid outer half-width

