fuel16 0.39218
helium 0.40005
zirc   0.45720
water

pin pf24
fuel24 0.39218
helium 0.40005
zirc   0.45720
water

pin pf31
fuel31 0.39218
helium 0.40005
zirc   0.45720
water

% guide tube (CR withdrawn -> water-filled) and narrowed dashpot thimble
pin pgt
water 0.56134
zirc  0.60198
water

pin pgtd
water 0.50419
zirc  0.54610
water

% instrument tube (air / Zr / water / Zr / water) and bare lower thimble
pin pit
air   0.43688
zirc  0.48387
water 0.56134
zirc  0.60198
water

pin pitb
air  0.43688
zirc 0.48387
water

% Pyrex burnable-poison pin (poison column, above dashpot)
pin pba
air    0.21400
ss304  0.23051
helium 0.24130
pyrex  0.42672
helium 0.43688
ss304  0.48387
water  0.56134
zirc   0.60198
water

% BA plenum geometry (above the poison column)
pin pbap
air    0.21400
ss304  0.23051
helium 0.43688
ss304  0.48387
water  0.50419
zirc   0.54610
water

% SS-filled guide tube / dashpot (BA lower transition)
pin pssgt
ss304 0.56134
zirc  0.60198
water

pin pssdp
ss304 0.50419
zirc  0.54610
water

% structural / plate / end-plug / plenum / water rods
pin pw
water

pin pss
ss304 0.45720
water

pin psps
supportss 0.45720
water

pin pspb
supportbw 0.45720
water

pin pzr
zirc 0.45720
water

pin pplen
inconel 0.06459
helium  0.40005
zirc    0.45720
water

% ===================== GRID-OVERLAY PIN UNIVERSES =====================
% Each = base pin + square Inconel grid sleeve (sGin -> sGout) in coolant.
cell f16g_1 uf16g fuel16  -sPel
cell f16g_2 uf16g helium  sPel -sGap
cell f16g_3 uf16g zirc    sGap -sClad
cell f16g_4 uf16g water   sClad -sGin
cell f16g_5 uf16g inconel sGin -sGout
cell f16g_6 uf16g water   sGout

cell f24g_1 uf24g fuel24  -sPel
